-- WRONG FILE if line 1 is {  = that is founder-brief.json (JSON). Do not paste JSON.
-- WRONG FILE if line 1 is import = that is seed-founder-brief.mjs (JavaScript).
-- RIGHT FILE: first line is -- (dash dash), then INSERT below.
